  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Cheval Blanc is an attractive ski in-ski out residence enjoying a quiet location in the lower part of the resort, with a good standard of comfort. It is ideal for the keen skier who wants to be on the slopes first thing in the morning.</p>
<h2>Great location</h2>
<p>The Cheval Blanc apartments have an excellent location in Val Thorens, providing keen skiers and snowboarders with ski in, ski out access to the fabulous <a data-udi="umb://document/72a5198213b1400d8c891f49fe57b578" href="/{localLink:umb://document/72a5198213b1400d8c891f49fe57b578}" title="Three Valleys Ski Area">Three Valleys Ski Area.</a> The resort centre is just a short walk away, where you can find a variety of shops and bars - there are some fantastic après spots to enjoy after a day of skiing. If you don't feel like cooking, there is also plenty of restaurants serving delicious Savoyard classics and family favourites including pizza, burgers and grilled meats. </p>
<h2>Comfortable apartments </h2>
<p>Furnished in a simplistic alpine design, these apartments provide a comfortable space to return to after a day of skiing. We have a range of apartments available, suitable for a group of family and friends looking for self-catered accommodation in <a data-udi="umb://document/bd152c97eb204c59a0ae4a5b65e2c1e5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/bd152c97eb204c59a0ae4a5b65e2c1e5}" title="France">France</a>. Many of the apartments have additional beds, so there is space for everyone. If you want to cook meals in the comfort of your apartment consider booking a <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/ski-holidays/special-offers/huski-food-drink-delivery-service">Huski</a> meal package, you can have breakfast and dinner delivered to your door - all you need to do is heat  the meals up. There is also plenty of restaurants in the resort for those evenings when you don't feel like cooking.</p>]]></description>
