  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>One Bedroom Apartments</strong> sleep two to four people and are around 27m². These apartments have an open plan kitchenette and living room with a double sofa bed, and a twin bedroom separated with a sliding door. </p>
<p><strong>Privilege One Bedroom Apartments</strong> sleep two to four people and are around 27m². These apartments are furnished to a high standard and have an open plan kitchenette and living room with a double sofa bed, and a twin bedroom.</p>
<p><strong>One Bedroom Cabin Apartments</strong> sleep two to six people and are around 33m². These apartments have an open plan kitchenette and living room with a double sofa bed, a twin bedroom separated with a sliding door, and a cabin room with bunk beds. </p>
<p><strong>Privilege One Bedroom Cabin Apartments</strong> sleep two to six people and are around 33m².  These apartments are furnished to a higher standard and have an open plan kitchenette and living room with a double sofa bed, a twin bedroom and cabin room with bunk beds. </p>
<p><strong>Three Bedroom Mezzanine Apartments</strong> sleep six to eight people and are around 50m². These duplex apartments have a open plan kitchenette and living room with a double sofa bed and additional twin beds or double sofa bed separated with a curtain or sliding door on the lower floor. Upstairs there is two open bedrooms, These apartments have two bathrooms. </p>
<p>Privilege apartments have a ski room with direct access to the slopes. Standard apartments will need to cross the street, from the ski room, to reach the slopes.</p>
<p><strong>Apartment facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Balcony with either village or mountain views</li>
<li>Wi-Fi</li>
<li>Satellite TV</li>
<li>Kitchenette with hot plates, oven, fridge, dishwasher, microwave, kitchenware</li>
<li>Tea and coffee making facilities</li>
<li>Safe</li>
<li>Telephone</li>
<li>Bed linen</li>
<li>Towels (mid-week change on request)</li>
<li>Cleaning kit <span>(sponge, dishware soap &amp; tablet, trash bags, duster)</span></li>
<li>Bathroom with shower head attachment or shower room</li>
<li>Baby cots are available on request. Free for children under 2 years old.</li>
<li>Baby safety gates are available (on request) from the reception</li>
<li>End of week cleaning is provided except for the kitchen and dishware, bins need to be taken out</li>
<li>Beds are made on arrival except sofa beds</li>
</ul>]]></roomsDescription>
